  "prompt": "How can I reset password of Instagram account without email?",
  "response": "There are several ways to reset an Instagram password without email:\n\n1. Using Phone Number\n- If you've linked a phone number to your account\n- Go to Instagram login page\n- Tap \"Forgot Password?\"\n- Select \"Send a code via SMS\"\n- Enter your phone number\n- Receive and enter verification code\n\n2. Through Facebook\n- If your Instagram is connected to Facebook\n- Go to Instagram login\n- Click \"Log in with Facebook\"\n- Use Facebook account credentials\n\n3. Using Username\n- Go to Instagram login page\n- Click \"Forgot Password?\"\n- Enter your username\n- Choose verification method\n\n4. Instagram Help Center\n- Visit Instagram Help Center\n- Submit account recovery request\n- Provide account details and identification\n\n5. Two-Factor Authentication\n- If enabled, use backup codes\n- Access through linked authentication app\n\nImportant Tips:\n- Provide accurate information\n- Have proof of account ownership\n- Be patient during verification process\n- Avoid multiple simultaneous recovery attempts\n\nRecommended Preventive Measures:\n- Keep contact information updated\n- Link multiple recovery methods\n- Use strong, unique password\n- Enable two-factor authentication\n\nNote: Actual recovery depends on specific account circumstances and Instagram's verification process.",
